import React from 'react';
import Layout from '../../components/Layout';
import { Container, Form, Button, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';





/** 
* @author
* @function Signin
**/



const Signin = (props) => {
    return (
        <Layout>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={{span:6, offset: 3}}>
                    <Form>
                    <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicEmail">
                        <Form.Label>Edresse Email</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="Entrer l'adresse email" />
                        <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                            Nous ne partageons jamais votre adresse email avec quelqu'un d'autre.
                        </Form.Text>
                    </Form.Group>

                    <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicPassword">
                        <Form.Label>Mot de passe</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="mot de passe" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
                        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="DÃ©couvrez-moi" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                        Envoyer
                    </Button>
                </Form>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
                
            </Container>
        </Layout>
    );
};

export default Signin;
